## podesavanje QT tema na GTK baziranom sistemu:
------------------------------------------------
   sudo apt-get install qt5-style-plugins
 1.Za QT 5 aplikacije:
   sudo su root
   sudo echo "QT_QPA_PLATFORMTHEME=gtk2" >> /etc/environment
   exit
 2. lxappearance (menu --> Settings --> Customize Look and Feel)
    Widget --> Arc-Dark
    Icon Theme --> Oxygen
 3. LogOut --> LogIn
